#################### Tips concerning WIFI Settings ####################

openwrt router login LuCI > network > wireless

edit ssid ("virtual" wireless interface) 2.4GHz and 5GHz > Advanced Settings
set country code = "IT - Italy" (it is an example, set your coutry code)
set coverage cell density = "Very High" --> minimum rate is 24Mbps, instead of 6Mbps

>>>>> Only wifi 5Ghz <<<<<
network > wireless > edit SSID 5Ghz > Interface configuration > Advanced Settings --> untick "Disassociate On Low Acknowledgement"


